data.description: Amazing mountaintop view from this home and 26.68 acres in Chester. Property is mostly wooded but has several clearings and some great building spots for additional homes. The house has plenty of space and could be 5 bedroom. Some recent kitchen updates. Huge covered back porch. Detached garage. Fenced yard and animal pen. House is currently on well water but city water is in the works for the area. Fiber Internet (Wave Rural Connect).
